remarks.summary: Störung.
remarks.text: Wegen Reparatur an der Strecke Ausfall RB18226 ab Flughafen BER - Terminal 5 (Schönefeld) (Abf. 18:19 Uhr). Nutzen Sie bitte den nachfolgenden RE8 ab Flughafen BER - Terminal 5 (Schönefeld) (Abf. 19:05 Uhr).

remarks.summary: Advance notice: Rail strike on Monday, 27 March
remarks.text: Due to a strike by the unions EVG and ver.di, there will be considerable restrictions. Almost all train journeys of RE, RB and S-Bahn trains will be cancelled, long-distance traffic will be completely cancelled. Underground trains, trams, buses and ferries will run. More details at www.vbb.de/streik.
